	<h2>
		User Experience and Design
	</h2>
	<p>
		Design is a fundamental part of any Palantir project. Good design not
 only seeks to inspire and engage users, but it should also communicate 
meaning and responsibility.
	</p>
	<p>
		We have a long history of collaborating with world-class designers on
 high-level, sophisticated Web projects. Our internal user experience 
(UX) team is experienced in developing design systems that not only 
seamlessly blend form and function, but also engage users as they 
interact with the site.
	</p>
	<p>
		In recent years, the Web has expanded beyond the desktop, with people
 increasingly using smartphones, tablets, and other devices to access 
information online. Whether it’s a standalone mobile app or a site that 
uses responsive design techniques, we can work with you to develop a 
user experience that takes into account all of the different ways that 
users might access your site.
	</p>
</p>
