experiences. We have adopted Drupal as our platform of choice because of
 its solid foundation, ease of implementation, and maximal 
extensibility.
	</p>
	<p>
		Palantir’s team includes many leading contributors to the Drupal 
software and community, and we have extensive experience building sites 
and mobile applications designed to meet the needs of companies and 
organizations of all sizes.
	</p>
	<p>
